"title": "5554: status",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5554: status",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A person's standing in society in the sight of others. The status of individuals in the sight of the world often differs radically from their status in the sight of God, but it is the latter that really matters.</p>\n<h2>Factors contributing to high social status</h2>\n<h3>High status associated with a position of secular authority</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:37-Dan2:38\">DAN 2:37–2:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:1-2Sam15:6\">2SA 15:1–15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:26-1Chr29:28\">1CH 29:26–29:28</a></p>\n<h3>High status based upon a position of domestic authority</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:6\">MAL 1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps123:2\">PSA 123:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:7-Luke17:10\">LUK 17:7–17:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:3\">1CO 11:3</a></p>\n<h3>High status owing to recognition of religious authority</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:34\">ACT 5:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:1-Matt23:2\">MAT 23:1–23:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:8-Matt23:10\">MAT 23:8–23:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:1-Acts23:5\">ACT 23:1–23:5</a></p>\n<h3>High status owing to pious conduct</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:5-Matt23:7\">MAT 23:5–23:7</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:38-Mark12:39\">MRK 12:38–12:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:45-Luke20:46\">LUK 20:45–20:46</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:2\">MAT 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:5\">MAT 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:16\">MAT 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:4-Luke7:5\">LUK 7:4–7:5</a></p>\n<h3>High status based on wealth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:4\">PRO 19:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:4-1Kgs10:7\">1KI 10:4–10:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:3-2Chr9:6\">2CH 9:3–9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:1-Job1:3\">JOB 1:1–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:1-Jas2:4\">JAS 2:1–2:4</a></p>\n<h2>Factors contributing to low social status</h2>\n<h3>Low status on account of occupation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:11\">MAT 9:11</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:16\">MRK 2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:30\">LUK 5:30</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:1-Luke15:2\">LUK 15:1–15:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:11\">LUK 18:11</a></p>\n<h3>Low status through sickness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:45-Lev13:46\">LEV 13:45–13:46</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:29-Matt20:31\">MAT 20:29–20:31</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:46-Mark10:48\">MRK 10:46–10:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:35-Luke18:39\">LUK 18:35–18:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:12-Luke17:13\">LUK 17:12–17:13</a></p>\n<h3>Low status through poverty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:11-Amos5:12\">AMO 5:11–5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:1-Job24:12\">JOB 24:1–24:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:20\">LUK 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:1-Jas2:4\">JAS 2:1–2:4</a></p>\n<h2>Status in God's kingdom</h2>\n<h3>The reversal of human status</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:3-Matt5:6\">MAT 5:3–5:6</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:20-Luke6:21\">LUK 6:20–6:21</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:13-Matt19:15\">MAT 19:13–19:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:13-Mark10:16\">MRK 10:13–10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:15-Luke18:17\">LUK 18:15–18:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:16-Matt19:30\">MAT 19:16–19:30</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:17-Mark10:31\">MRK 10:17–10:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:18-Luke18:30\">LUK 18:18–18:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:52-Luke1:53\">LUK 1:52–1:53</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:19-Luke16:26\">LUK 16:19–16:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:26-1Cor1:29\">1CO 1:26–1:29</a></p>\n<h3>Believers must take the lowest status</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:1-Matt18:5\">MAT 18:1–18:5</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:33-Mark9:37\">MRK 9:33–9:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:46-Luke9:48\">LUK 9:46–9:48</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:20-Matt20:28\">MAT 20:20–20:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:35-Mark10:45\">MRK 10:35–10:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:7-Luke14:11\">LUK 14:7–14:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:12-John13:15\">JHN 13:12–13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:3-Phil2:5\">PHP 2:3–2:5</a></p>\n<h3>All believers enjoy equal status before God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:28\">GAL 3:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:22\">1CO 7:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:11-1Cor11:12\">1CO 11:11–11:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:15-Phlm1:17\">PHM 1:15–1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:9-Jas1:10\">JAS 1:9–1:10</a></p>",
